Suggests: ydotool, playerctl, speech-dispatcher
Description: Shortcuts and automations for your desktop
 Lightning is a free, open-source, cross-platform app for building
 drag-and-drop shortcuts and event-driven automations: schedules, file
 watches, Wi-Fi events, USB devices, clipboard changes and more.
 .
 Optional tools unlock more actions at runtime (honest capability
 probing): ydotool for input injection on Wayland, playerctl for media
 control, speech-dispatcher for text-to-speech.
